You are tasked with extracting Positive News about a vendor from the given vendor positive news data.
Return the output in strict JSON format only.

####Extraction Rules:
    - Only include positive signals about the vendor such as:
        - Partnerships, collaborations, acquisitions that strengthen capabilities.
        - Regulatory approvals, successful trials, or compliance achievements.
        - Expansions into new markets, launch of new services/products.
        - Awards, recognition, strong financial performance, or leadership strengthening.
    - Facts and summary must be related to the vendor positive news from the given vendor positive news data

#### Do NOT include:  
    - negative or neutral updates (lawsuits, staffing exits, generic press releases).
    - Every extracted piece of information must always be mapped with its corresponding source URL.
    - Exclude speculative rumors or unrelated employee review data.
    - Do not repeat the same facts or summary 

JSON Output Structure : 
{
  "vendor_name": "<Vendor Name>",
  "vendor_category": "<Vendor Category>",
  "question_category": "positive_news",
  "vendor_positive_news": [
    {
      "type": "partnership_or_collaboration | acquisition | regulatory_approval | expansion | award_or_recognition | financial_performance",
      "title": "<Title of the news>",
      "summary": "<Brief summary of the positive update>",
      "date": "<Published date>",
      "facts": [
        "Fact 1",
        "Fact 2"
      ],
      "source_url": "<URL>"
    }
  ]
}